{"tid":985190,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想同大家分享一個心靈勵志既故事","createTime":"2019-01-17T11:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T11:40:37.000Z","uid":65256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0338ec382a85aa6d282c5ce1fbb36c216d315fa9","tid":985190,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T11:36:50.000Z","msg":"一隻烏鴉口渴了，到處找水喝。<br />\n<br />\n烏鴉看見一個瓶子。瓶子裏有水，可是瓶子很高，瓶口很小，裏邊的水又少，它喝不了水。怎麽辦呢?<br />\n<br />\n烏鴉看見旁邊有許多小石子，它想一想，有辦法了!<br />\n<br />\n烏鴉把小石子一個一個地銜起來，放到瓶子裏。瓶子裏的水慢慢升高，烏鴉就喝著水了。"},{"pid":"c4d85181d301231d88216fe33c65ec498b2b7b94","tid":985190,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T11:37:34.000Z","msg":"口喝了"},{"pid":"a93bb1a89e86e5386e1ee66db26d81f243ed5a22","tid":985190,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4d85181d301231d88216fe33c65ec498b2b7b94","tid":985190,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T11:37:34.000Z","msg":"口喝了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T11:38:01.000Z","msg":"飲水"},{"pid":"32fc2862da221d4cdaf937217200aeefc53cbd4d","tid":985190,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a93bb1a89e86e5386e1ee66db26d81f243ed5a22","tid":985190,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4d85181d301231d88216fe33c65ec498b2b7b94","tid":985190,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T11:37:34.000Z","msg":"口喝了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T11:38:01.000Z","msg":"飲水"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T11:38:26.000Z","msg":"木水"},{"pid":"5da4df239b822fd346f3c104913bc92a2e38fde0","tid":985190,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32fc2862da221d4cdaf937217200aeefc53cbd4d","tid":985190,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a93bb1a89e86e5386e1ee66db26d81f243ed5a22","tid":985190,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4d85181d301231d88216fe33c65ec498b2b7b94","tid":985190,"uid":35105,"like